      "Inconsistent error-policy boundaries around event publishing/runtime preparation across modules",
      "Asymmetric API contracts that sometimes expose setup failures and sometimes intentionally suppress them"
    ],
    "likely_symptoms": [
      "Silent runtime fallback causing production startup misconfigurations to appear non-fatal",
      "Debugging shutdown/startup issues in Wi‑Fi subsystem becomes difficult because stop failures are not observable"
    ],
    "possible_false_positives": [
